{"tid":8326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「法國版戴卓爾」勝出初選 成為共和黨總統候選人","createTime":"2016-11-28T10:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T09:22:44.000Z","uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aaff985153f84d8926b71dc1b9caf2d80c092faa","tid":8326,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1X61nX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1X61nX.jpg&h=deaf699e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國保守派共和黨（Les R&eacute;publicains）黨內初選第二輪投票完成，前總理Fran&ccedil;ois Fillon以66.5%勝出，一般預測他頗大機會勝出2017年總統大選。<br />\n<br />\n他將對決主張脫離歐盟的國民陣線（Front National）主席瑪麗勒龐&mdash;&mdash;形成保守派與極右派之間的廝殺，左派越趨邊緣化。<br />\n<br />\n初選首輪投票20日由波爾多市長Alain Juppe、前總統薩爾科齊、Fillon等候選人競逐，薩爾科齊得票率第三遭淘汰，Fillon與Juppe晉級第二輪。<br />\n<br />\n上周開始的初選，是共和黨為消除內鬥而歷來首度採取美國式黨內初選，全國4400萬選民中有400多萬人參加。<br />\n<br />\n62歲的Fillon曾由薩爾科齊提名出任總理（2007-2012），他曾讚賞前英國首相戴卓爾夫人和挑戰工會而被稱為「法國的戴卓爾」。他立場中間偏右，承諾維護傳統家庭價值與「法蘭西價值」。<br />\n<br />\n當選總統後外交將與俄羅斯保持聯繫，舉行配額公投將移民人數減到最少，削減預算1100億歐元，大砍公務員數目，將退休年齡從62歲提高到65歲，延長目前的每周35小時工作時間，以及放寬勞工法律以方便僱主。<br />\n<br />\n對於近年棘手的恐怖主義和難民問題，亦主張強硬的應對手段；讓Fillon獲得不少保守右派裡面中高年齡層的支持。"},{"pid":"0fda3ef39ae94bdc624276efde382e8e0f9d1d4f","tid":8326,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:32:40.000Z","msg":"全球右傾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0f1aa45ac3bcacc72234c618ff2a7740469eb2","tid":8326,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ff3fbc2fe09f62702d1bfd7dfdb820b7eeb3f7","tid":8326,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"右對極右 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d099c9d27fc27ca25160ca9e481da3314b68e607","tid":8326,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全球右傾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國人恨到啦 右翼勢力抬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe7ddbd048dc300c2852c96dbcc6882861b3984","tid":8326,"uid":35686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"里昂 &ndash; 法國前總理菲永在中右翼總統出現選情看漲，不少電視畫面都顯示他的支持者很多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但有網民踢爆，他在里昂的造勢大會其實人數不足，本來book了一個大場，但半個場是空的，電視畫面只是在前半場拍的。<br />\n<br />\n瑞士法文20分鐘報  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要睇定d wor<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gaus.ee/2016/11/fillon-fake-popu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2F2016%2F11%2Ffillon-fake-popu%2F&d=REILfn9PG8J42kYIDykZ0MW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=b7ba06e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://gaus.ee/2016/11/fillon-fake-popu/</a>"},{"pid":"6991acdba1fee2adfa3a643a6c22ce00e050c1ef","tid":8326,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb90252fcbfe61796a4377af4bc49993ed3dad1","tid":8326,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"極右先係黑天鵝"}]}